= dsgame demo
Nintendo DS Game Demo includes Lua.

== requirements
 * devkitARM r27
 * libnds 1.4.0
 * libfat-nds 1.0.6
 * dswifi 0.3.11
 * libfilesystem 0.9.4
 * maxmod-nds 1.0.6
 * default.arm7 0.5.8
  - http://www.devkitpro.org/
 * PAlib 0912XX
  - http://palib-dev.com/
 * lua-5.1.4
  - http://www.lua.org/
 * DeSmuME 0.9.5
  - http://desmume.org/
 * GBA Movie Player (Compact Flash) DLDI, dlditool
  - http://chishm.drunkencoders.com/DLDI/
  

== build
 * setup devkitPro and PAlib
 * copy lua-5.1.4/ to dsgame/source
 * remove lua.c, luac.c from dsgame/source/lua-5.1.4/src
 * execute build.bat

== run
 * copy DeSmuME_dev.exe, mpcf.dldi, dlditool.exe to dsgame/
 * execute run.bat
